elements.description:
`coronita-icons` is a utility import that includes the definition for the `iron-icon` element, `iron-iconset-svg` element, as well as an import for the default icon set, which is `coronita-icons`.

Example using default coronita-icons family:

```html
  <link rel="import" href="../coronita-icons/coronita-icons.html">
  <iron-icon icon="account"></iron-icon>
```

See [iron-iconset](#iron-iconset) and [iron-iconset-svg](#iron-iconset-svg) for more information about how to create a custom iconset.

Available icon families:
- coronita-icons
